le, and returns to her initial state whenever she is defeated. Any progress she has made during the run is lost, leaving only the notes she records in her diary.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886540/extras/b4eba204b8af739324f98ae9b6dd2447.poster.avif?t=1747252168\" width=629 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886540/extras/b4eba204b8af739324f98ae9b6dd2447.webm?t=1747252168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
